(e) require the Property Officer to diligently prepare/maintain inventory records such as SCs and PCs, Monthly Report of Supplies and Materials Issued, RIS and Inventory List of all procured and donated items and coordinate with the Accounting Office for the periodic reconciliation of both inventory records; and

(f) provide storage/stockroom located in accessible, safe and secured areas that will accommodate all supplies, medicines, materials, equipment and relief goods of the MDRRMO to avoid possible loss and physical quality deterioration and can immediately response in times of calamities.

