We recommended that the Local Chief Executive direct the Municipal Solid Waste Management to:

(a) transport the solid wastes within 24 hours from the staging area/transfer station to Metro Clark Waste Management; operate the Municipal MRF; and maximize utilization of the Plastic Pulverizer to prevent the accumulation of solid wastes in the staging area and lessen the plastic wastes;

